## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="7d206-297">集合中的默认实现<xref:System.Collections.Generic?displayProperty=nameWithType>不同步。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7d206-297">Default implementations of collections in <xref:System.Collections.Generic?displayProperty=nameWithType> are not synchronized.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7d206-298">枚举整个集合本质上不是一个线程安全的过程。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7d206-298">Enumerating through a collection is intrinsically not a thread-safe procedure.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7d206-299">若要确保枚举过程中的线程安全性，可以在整个枚举过程中锁定集合。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7d206-299">To guarantee thread safety during enumeration, you can lock the collection during the entire enumeration.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="7d206-300">若要允许多个线程访问集合以进行读写操作，则必须实现自己的同步。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7d206-300">To allow the collection to be accessed by multiple threads for reading and writing, you must implement your own synchronization.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7d206-301"><xref:System.Collections.ICollection.SyncRoot%2A> 返回可以用于对访问进行同步的对象<xref:System.Collections.ICollection>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7d206-301"><xref:System.Collections.ICollection.SyncRoot%2A> returns an object that can be used to synchronize access to the <xref:System.Collections.ICollection>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7d206-302">同步是仅当所有线程在访问该集合之前都锁定此对象有效。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7d206-302">Synchronization is effective only if all threads lock this object before accessing the collection.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7d206-303">下面的代码演示如何使用<xref:System.Collections.ICollection.SyncRoot%2A>C#、 Visual c + + 和 Visual Basic 的属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7d206-303">The following code shows the use of the <xref:System.Collections.ICollection.SyncRoot%2A> property for C#, Visual C++, and Visual Basic.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
ICollection ic = ...;  
lock (ic.SyncRoot) {  
   // Access the collection.  
}  
```  
  
```vb  
Dim ic As ICollection = ...  
SyncLock ic.SyncRoot  
   ' Access the collection.  
End SyncLock  
```  
  
```cpp#  
ICollection^ ic = ...;  
try {  
   Monitor::Enter(ic->SyncRoot);  
   // Access the collection.  
}  
finally {  
   Monitor::Exit(ic->SyncRoot);  
}  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7d206-304">检索此属性的值的运算复杂度为 O(1)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7d206-304">Retrieving the value of this property is an O(1) operation.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7d206-305">此成员是显式的接口成员实现。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7d206-305">This member is an explicit interface member implementation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7d206-306">它只能在 <xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyCollection%601> 实例强制转换为 <xref:System.IDisposable> 接口时使用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7d206-306">It can be used only when the <xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyCollection%601> instance is cast to an <xref:System.IDisposable> interface.</span></span>
